snippet.title: Best VGM 1784 - Shenmue - Tomato Convenience Store
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 301 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_OguBY5x-Qo
Best VGM 535 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dlZyjOv5G80
Best VGM 1046 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qnvYRm_8Oy8
Best VGM 1600 - http://youtu.be/CgtvppDEyeU
Best VGM 1999 - https://youtu.be/Tug0cYK0XW0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Dreamcast
Shenmue (2000)
Tomato Convenience Store
Osamu Murata, Ryuji Iuchi, Takenobu Mitsuyoshi, Takeshi Yanagawa & Yuzo Koshiro
